scene.message:
Principal Oishi: Oh, {ctl0f:1}.{waitkey}...{wait_fr:32}Did something happen?{nl}
Don't tell me the girl in{nl}
black appeared again?!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: No, that's not it,{nl}
Principal. But this girl in{nl}
black...?{waitkey}{ret}

Vice Principal Hannya: News{nl}
to you, Nanjo? Lately a girl{nl}
in black's been showing up{nl}
at this school...{waitkey}And they say she commands{nl}
demons.{waitkey}{ret}

Vice Principal Hannya: But{nl}
there's no need to worry.{waitkey}{clearbox}Principal Oishi and I will{nl}
protect you students, you'll{nl}
see!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Wh-what's with that?{nl}
Creeps me out!{waitkey}{clearbox}Why's old Hannya being so{nl}
nice?! A-anyway, let's get{nl}
out of here!{waitkey}{ret}

Vice Principal Hannya: Oh,{nl}
thank goodness...{waitkey}But what in the world was{nl}
that? The whole school seemed{nl}
to fall into utter chaos...{waitkey}{ret}

Vice Principal Hannya: Did you{nl}
hear that, Principal? What{nl}
compassion...{waitkey}{clearbox}Principal, this too is the{nl}
fruit of your wonderful{nl}
education!{waitkey}{ret}

Principal Oishi: No, no, Vice{nl}
Principal. It's thanks to{nl}
your guidance!{waitkey}{ret}

{color:3}Principal Oishi{nl}
The principal of St. Hermelin{nl}
Academy. A woman who loves{nl}
children and flowers.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Vice Principal Hannya{nl}
Known as "Hannya." His strict{nl}
discipline should make him{nl}
disliked by students, but...{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}
